  "title": "AIKernel Semantic DSL Compiler and Deterministic Agent Execution Architecture",
  "upload_type": "publication",
  "publication_type": "technicalnote",
  "description": "This technical note introduces the AIKernel Semantic DSL Compiler, an OS-level mechanism for governing probabilistic LLM-generated plans through deterministic compilation rather than direct execution. The compilation path is Semantic IR -> Admissibility Checking -> Governed Pipeline -> ResultStep / SemanticDelta -> hash-linked ReplayLog. The English manuscript is canonical; the Japanese manuscript is included as a companion translation.",
